      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Simple Nomenclator Query Protocol (SNQP) allows a client to communicate with a descriptive name service or other relational-style query service.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard of any kind&lt;/p&gt;</t>
